                <p>Effective management practices to keep ducks healthy:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Grooming:</strong> Regularly check ducks for injuries and keep their living area clean.</li>
                    <li><strong>Exercise:</strong> Provide ample space for ducks to forage, swim, and exercise.</li>
                    <li><strong>Healthcare:</strong> Implement a routine health check, including vaccinations and parasite control.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Establish a daily care routine to monitor the health and behavior of your ducks.</p>
            </div>
